    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras/81951d7ec4898b710a62d3064f0435cd.avif?t=1771944795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras_big/81951d7ec4898b710a62d3064f0435cd.webp?t=1771944795 width=1560 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >█ 《ROUTINE》是一款第一人称科幻恐怖游戏，故事发生在基于80年代未来主义兴建，但如今已然废弃的月球基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当月球基地陷入死寂，好奇探索便化作生存渴望。追寻答案的过程中，不得不与某位将你视作眼中钉的敌手狭路相逢。调查越是深入，真相越是扑朔迷离——除了继续向前，别无他法。▌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：《ROUTINE》中不提供路径标识，寻路也是游戏体验的一部分。放慢脚步，仔细观察周边环境，不放过任何一处探索细节，用数据开拓前路。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras/1184551c8a284c2edb0100f23dff7d07.poster.avif?t=1771944795\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras/1184551c8a284c2edb0100f23dff7d07.webm?t=1771944795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras/1184551c8a284c2edb0100f23dff7d07.mp4?t=1771944795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >█ 探索：月球基地内设立了风格迥异的多个区域，从年久失修的居住区和电车站入手，一路摸排至废弃商场。▌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >█ 观察：调查周边环境，掌握关键信息才能步步深入，拼凑出你抵达前这里发生的一切。▌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >█ 沉浸：全身感知、画内音频，外加极简UI，共同打造出扣人心弦的游戏体验，氛围感十足。▌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >█ 操作：你的随身C.A.T.（宇航员辅助工具）可谓至关重要，可用于访问关键终端、环境导航与线索识别。▌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >█ 生存：面对未知威胁，或奋力奔跑，或谨慎藏匿——走投无路时，C.A.T.便是你的最终武器。 ▌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras/01b19fa30a98b76d9b56d3e4606cf0e7.avif?t=1771944795\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/606160/extras_big/01b19fa30a98b76d9b56d3e4606cf0e7.webp?t=1771944795 width=1560 height=853 /></span></p>",
